summary: This mod improved the Tavern Clothings in the game with zero fps hit.
descriptionHtml:
Another mod, another texture improvement with zero fps hit. This time, i have made the
Tavern Cloths more crisp in details and improved normal mapping. The next update will have the male Tavarn Clothing improved.
-----Installation------

Place the Textures folder into your Skyrim data game folder. or let your Nexus Mod Manager fix it for you.
------

Got any critics? Or maybe want to add something random? Feel free to post it in the comment section ;)

---To do---
